Bildad okwer ni dhano ok nyal bedo maler e nyim Nyasaye


1  Bang’ wechego Bildad nowacho niya,


2  “Nyasaye nigi teko mathoth, omiyo ji duto nyaka luore.

Orito polo gi kue.


3  Bende nitie ng’at manyalo kwano malaika ma tiyone?

Koso nitie kamoro ma ler mar Nysaye ok rienyie?


4  Bende nitie ng’at manyalo bet makare kata maler e wang’ Nyasaye?


5  Ka Nyasaye ok kwan kata mana due ka gima rieny ahinya,

kendo ka ok okwan sulue ka gik maler adier,


6  to koro dhano mana ma kudni akudani, to dichal nade e nyime?”

